paragraph: Aline Barros Kistenmacker dos Santos (born October 7, 1976), better known as Aline Barros is a singer, songwriter, presenter and manager in Brazil. Some of her albums have been certified multiple Diamond by the Associação Brasileira dos Produtores de Discos (ABPD).
Aline Barros played Snow White, the movie Aline Barros: Escola de Princesas
The following discography is limited to albums which were certified by the Associação Brasileira dos Produtores de Discos (ABPD).
Aline Barros: Escola de Princesas - Snow White
